  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756160/extras/0bd59b473246be0a2d02d539e414a45a.webp?t=1763472714\" width=616 height=38 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><i> Hastur Industries</i> <i>is hiring!</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Join our forces and experience a unique adventure throughout space!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Explore new worlds and meet new beings, all while (sometimes) getting paid!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756160/extras/d3511369b3cd36d583b8f26d7219955f.poster.avif?t=1763472714\" width=616 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756160/extras/d3511369b3cd36d583b8f26d7219955f.webm?t=1763472714\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756160/extras/d3511369b3cd36d583b8f26d7219955f.mp4?t=1763472714\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756160/extras/aa20e5ab3f1a8fa5a97a454d3610126b.webp?t=1763472714\" width=616 height=38 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756160/extras/b1c990cf67a1ebe9ad32ab89baf7a58f.poster.avif?t=1763472714\" width=616 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756160/extras/b1c990cf67a1ebe9ad32ab89baf7a58f.webm?t=1763472714\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756160/extras/b1c990cf67a1ebe9ad32ab89baf7a58f.mp4?t=1763472714\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Use the terminal to <i>navigate</i> the galaxy with the company's interstellar train. Access various space stations full of materials, mysterious lifeforms and other horrors that lurk in the dark corners of humanity's ever-reaching grip into the darkness of space.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756160/extras/8443e6e099551a9b25301801aea73338.webp?t=1763472714\" width=616 height=38 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756160/extras/90e190b740b64521bba79f4f7554a29c.poster.avif?t=1763472714\" width=616 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756160/extras/90e190b740b64521bba79f4f7554a29c.webm?t=1763472714\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756160/extras/90e190b740b64521bba79f4f7554a29c.mp4?t=1763472714\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><i>Gather</i> the necessary materials for your mission, but remember; you are not alone  out there... There are many entities out there who seek to curb humanity's progress.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756160/extras/73de01e4db0b577f469f416aa1a8112c.webp?t=1763472714\" width=616 height=38 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756160/extras/b2176c6aca323d5899f9aabc0ec52d98.poster.avif?t=1763472714\" width=616 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756160/extras/b2176c6aca323d5899f9aabc0ec52d98.webm?t=1763472714\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756160/extras/b2176c6aca323d5899f9aabc0ec52d98.mp4?t=1763472714\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Sell materials to <i>complete</i> your mission. Earn some profit on the side and remind yourself how lucky you are to work for a company that values profit over human life! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756160/extras/8b4513821f3550de18101258962f2a93.webp?t=1763472714\" width=616 height=38 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Take note, you must fulfill each mission within 3 days. Plan your space station exploration carefully! Failure to deliver your quota and your future with Hastur Industries may come into question. There are always more like you, who will continue the holy work of capitalism should you fail however, so have fun, and may the force of profit be with you! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756160/extras/ab3e23065a329c3f3fe488cdbe707938.poster.avif?t=1763472714\" width=616 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756160/extras/ab3e23065a329c3f3fe488cdbe707938.webm?t=1763472714\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756160/extras/ab3e23065a329c3f3fe488cdbe707938.mp4?t=1763472714\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756160/extras/1511613a456f88c063034fb9fd3c8052.webp?t=1763472714\" width=616 height=38 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 1-4 PLAYER ONLINE COOP</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > PROXIMITY VOICE CHAT</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > MANY TOOLS AND ITEMS TO CHOOSE FROM</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > CUSTOMIZE YOUR CHARACTER</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > YOU MUST PET THE CAT</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > TRAUMATIC EXPERIENCES WITH ALIEN LIFEFORMS (BONUS!)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > CREATIVE WAYS TO DIE</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > NOT SO MANY CREATIVE WAYS TO KILL</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756160/extras/9cd9cd176f28cb1ccbdfafd28eeb7a88.poster.avif?t=1763472714\" width=616 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756160/extras/9cd9cd176f28cb1ccbdfafd28eeb7a88.webm?t=1763472714\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756160/extras/9cd9cd176f28cb1ccbdfafd28eeb7a88.mp4?t=1763472714\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756160/extras/5c22a1cccd054a1730e18009bcdd4a4c.webp?t=1763472714\" width=616 height=38 /></span></p>",
